onduras </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Ecuador </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Peru </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Brazil </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> El </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Salvador </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Nicaragua </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Spain </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Argentina </LOCATION> and the <LOCATION> Dominican </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Republic </LOCATION>. <LOCATION> South </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Korea </LOCATION>, the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Norway </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Switzerland </LOCATION> and were represented as observers.
